parameters:
Passerby: I-I was just walking down the street, wondering if
there might be any cute female students around...

Passerby: Gya-------!!! W-what the hell is this thing...
gah...

Classmate: Please, don't hit me... I'm happy to see
Sameyama-san in her underwear, but why do I have to be
stripped naked on the side of the road...

Vice President of the Student Council: Why are you doing
this...? Could it be that you've discovered I rub my cheek
on the chair in the student council room every day after
President Memimi has sat there...?

Vice President of the Student Council: Guuuaaah... Please
forgive me...!
Memimi: Let's go home... or not... see you next time~
Passerby: They left... huh, what was that all about...?

Male Student: Monsters are scary... you never know what
they'll do, so I won't tell anyone about today...
Chairman: Gah!? What's the matter, Shark Broccoli-kun...
